*2010年：玫瑰學苑拆除爭議<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/32532722/IssueID/20100523 |title=玫瑰學苑拆除爭議 |accessdate=2010-07-08 |archive-date=2010-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526021651/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/32532722/IssueID/20100523 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
